Проверка гипотез¶

Средние пользовательские рейтинги платформ Xbox One и PC одинаковые¶

:

  • H0 - Xbox One PC
  • H1 - Xbox One PC
In [37]:
#    
xbox_tt = df_top_pl.query('platform == "XOne" and user_score >= 0')['user_score']
pc_tt = df_top_pl.query('platform == "PC" and user_score >= 0')['user_score']

# 
alpha = .05
#     ttest_ind
results = st.ttest_ind(pc_tt, xbox_tt, equal_var=False)
print('p-:', results.pvalue)
if (results.pvalue < alpha):
    print("  ")
else:
    print("    ")

p-: 0.14759594013430463

, Xone PC

Средние пользовательские рейтинги жанров Action и Sports разные¶

:

  • H0 - Action Sports
  • H1 - Action Sports
In [38]:
#    
action_tt = df_top_pl.query('genre == "Action" and user_score >= 0')['user_score']
sports_tt = df_top_pl.query('genre == "Sports" and user_score >= 0')['user_score']

# 
alpha = .05
#     ttest_ind
results = st.ttest_ind(action_tt, sports_tt, equal_var=False)
print('p-:', results.pvalue)
if (results.pvalue < alpha):
    print("  ")
else:
    print("    ")

p-: 1.2678091455806196e-11

, "Action" "Sports"
